column5: 9,000 posts??? I'm just thrilled to death to know that I'm not the only one on the board with no life! Good on ya Chris.
The board of 10,000 posts...  That is the average number of posts you need before you land the big one...?   Not sure what the big one is here.. but I bet it gives a good fight...!
Well your sort of right Roy, I do have a life, sad as it may be. It's three feet away from the puter desk to the rod building & flytying desk.
Holy mackeral......!  I'm all the way up to #57...!
Way to go Captain !!!  And how is the lovely Mrs Leslie ?
Clearly she's busy keeping Kevin away from the computer....
Hang in there capt! You'll start to notice new facial hair at #100.
